column3: [' (StepDescription: add-Extract and add contents of an egg to a microwave-safe bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Place-Place 8 inch tortilla on a cutting board)']
[' (StepDescription: Add-Add 1/2 tbsp sweet and sour sauce to the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Add-Add 1 tbsp salsa to the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Mix-Mix the contents of the bowl well)']
[' (StepDescription: Pour-Pour egg mixture on top of the tortilla)']
[' (StepDescription: Pour-Pour egg mixture on top of the tortilla)']
[' (StepDescription: Sprinkle-Sprinkle 1 tbsp shredded cheddar cheese on top of the egg)']
[' (StepDescription: Roll-Roll the tortilla from one end to another into a log shape
column4: about 1.5 inches thick. Roll it tight enough to prevent gaps but not so tight that the filling leaks)']
